<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .booking-details {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .serial-key {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px dashed #ddd;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .note {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Booking Confirmation</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Dear {{guestName}},</p>

    <p>Your booking has been confirmed. Here are your booking details:</p>

    <div class="booking-details">
        <p><strong>Serial Key:</strong></p>
        <div class="serial-key">{{serialKey}}</div>
        
        <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong><br>
        {{formatDate startTime}}<br>
        From: {{formatTime startTime}}<br>
        To: {{formatTime endTime}}</p>
        
        <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} minutes</p>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
        <p>Important:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Please keep your serial key safe - you'll need it for any changes or cancellations</li>
            <li>Arrive at least 5 minutes before your scheduled time</li>
            <li>If you need to cancel or reschedule, please do so at least 24 hours in advance</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <p>If you have any questions or need to make changes to your booking, please contact us with your serial key as reference.</p>

    <p>Thank you for choosing our service!</p>

    <hr>
    <p class="note">This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
</body>
</html>
